title: Frenemies #2 - Trisha's Obsession With Jewish People
description: Welcome back for episode #2 of Frenemies! People (unironically this time) said we wouldn't be back, but we've defied the odds. Together Ethan and Trisha recap her visit to Ethan's house for a Jewish Holiday, plastic surgery, drugs, and a whole lot more!
